flowRoot.flowPara: Recursion for generating the worst case of constraints
1) choose point 1 above the black line
2) choose point 2 above the blue dashed line
4) Save two constraints, one generated from the pink line and one from the line connecting point 1 and point 2 (not shown)
5) Change the pink objects' color to black and remove the rest, go back to step 1.
Going beyond 6 such triangles is difficult in a drawing
